{"tid":1702264,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人，唔好轉移仇恨","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T15:39:26.000Z","uid":48044,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"627a9174f4c79f5e3ecc2b708e7f87cf2cf30497","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\">過左咁多日，已經有無數既核彈浮上水面，而且我相信只係冰山一角，對我黎講已經憎到極點，雖然咁樣平日好辛苦，但我堅持每次發夢既時候發洩。不過發夢時候，手足人數都少左，除左係因為被捕之外，我認為有另一個原因，就係將憤怒用錯地方。</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">根據我所見所聞，我發現好多人識得轉移仇恨，令自己下火。例如：開ig/fb發洩，同藍絲/屋企人嘈交等等，呢啲行為多數係你負面情緒去到極點既時候出現，但當你做完之後，透過咁既渠道釋放左你既負面情緒，咁你既仇恨就會減少繼而行動力下降，我相信，憤怒係好強大既推動力。而且事實上，黑警同政權根本冇少到一忽肉，相反行動人數又少左，手足既公義亦都得唔到伸張。</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">我係一個香港人，所以好撚小氣，一定同你計到盡，絕對唔會忘記。君子報仇十年未晚，不過我唔希望要等十年，我想短期之內可以見到港共同香港警察被清算。而要達成呢個結果，好需要大家保持心入面既情緒，千其唔好釋放喺冇效果既渠道。近排同黎緊既日子，相信大家既情緒都會有起伏，希望大家睇到我既諗法之後，會有新既體會。希望大家發洩既環境係響夢境入面，身邊唔單止會有手足支持，亦係最有效既渠道達成你所想既結果，完事後，無論身邊既人定係自己都會身心舒暢。</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">利申：本人唔支持暴力，雖然暴力係可以直接抒發情緒，但可能會令維持治安既警察同無辜市民受到嚴重傷害。</div>"},{"pid":"afa364f230ead92ec22d31b9d07eb70b2ff18a91","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"db236b08aaf48436734fcf00db17e26e26ee3d62","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"認同請分享，然後用於行動之上"},{"pid":"1f70c3057e1884cefc986e0bb95b5c154d43e124","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"女姦男殺已出現"},{"pid":"a590359c9e69e108e926924fd385b24ccc33ce9a","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"警甴尋晚話開香檳慶祝"},{"pid":"79f87a1d3efbdce167dc7f4758a0ea60b482aadf","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"跳樓全棵冇可疑"},{"pid":"637dac49348762f956fd0c8869f4e12328853370","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"跳海全棵都冇可疑"},{"pid":"fbd50ddb7feda340c8042775dc523af2ff5c8119","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"鐳射筆係攻擊性武器，罪名成立"},{"pid":"636f7456e810915a1767c5c549fd4ae04264682b","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"聽日同11/11，反抗"},{"pid":"d89e5a02815c94841b5ead38e543a32a202bbd89","tid":1702264,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8816652c8119d6b01d7fb8dbe3ce8e9a9c39af6e","tid":1702264,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvr5oqM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frvr5oqM.jpg&h=a04ec70b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=9bcaa18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a><br />\n公海: <a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielamgroup&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=df98612c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielamgroup</a><br />\n九龍西分區: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=5ddb11fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LC07DRSKGRrfozKTM3at-A</a><br />\n九龍